Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.06,0:02:59.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉与桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.06,0:03:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.83,0:03:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.87,0:03:08.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.77,0:03:13.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.36,0:03:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第48话 想回到相遇的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.16,0:03:37.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.30,0:03:40.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何你目不转睛的盯着我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.97,0:03:44.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.19,0:04:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些是防止化脓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:07.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些是止痛的涂抹药
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.90,0:04:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  纱布与绷带我带了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.04,0:04:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  那么我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:19.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.34,0:04:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又要回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:25.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是送药过来而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.38,0:04:29.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  至少和犬夜叉握手言和
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.25,0:04:30.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再为了小事就吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.42,0:04:36.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和犬夜叉吵过架
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.43,0:04:40.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在怎么想都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.43,0:04:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但怎能将你交给奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能从奈落手里保护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:47.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我而已不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:58.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵架的事我居然完全忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.42,0:05:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.72,0:05:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇无精打采的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.56,0:05:13.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉…这也不是没有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.57,0:05:20.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个光是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.24,0:05:29.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:36.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  戈薇姑娘又回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.39,0:05:38.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:44.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  你和桔梗见面了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.69,0:05:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且让戈薇姑娘看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.76,0:05:49.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.17,0:05:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…被看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.40,0:05:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你还厚着脸皮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.84,0:06:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  你满面佛光喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  那种大彻大悟的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.80,0:06:27.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉目不转睛的盯着我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.80,0:06:32.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉似乎打算说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.44,0:06:35.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但因为我害怕听见而逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉一定下定决心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:43.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.95,0:06:45.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉与桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:47.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因奈落的陷阱而彼此憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:51.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗亦追随犬夜叉而死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:55.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且拆散两人的奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.96,0:06:57.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再度袭击桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.77,0:07:02.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在怎么想都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.74,0:07:05.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但怎能将你交给奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.41,0:07:07.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能保护你的只有我而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.68,0:07:14.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就没有我介入的余地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:26.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然我还是放不下桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.93,0:07:28.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.20,0:07:32.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  我已经不会再见你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.63,0:07:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不能再见你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.50,0:07:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗为了犬夜叉\N连命都豁出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.01,0:07:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我根本比不上她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.95,0:07:48.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再也无法回到犬夜叉那里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.31,0:08:14.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉也不会来接我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.55,0:08:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.42,0:08:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把四魂碎片带来这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:29.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是还给他比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.43,0:08:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错…把这个还回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.00,0:08:38.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后一切都会结束
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.63,0:08:43.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我则回到普通的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么早就回来不说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.09,0:09:06.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从回来之后又都不说话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.66,0:09:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐是怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.96,0:09:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原因是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.80,0:09:14.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大拇指?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.97,0:09:16.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋  是男人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.97,0:09:21.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和犬夜叉哥哥吵架了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.38,0:09:25.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈…\N爸爸  方便的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:28.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这份荷包蛋给你吃好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.48,0:09:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.72,0:09:32.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:36.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.49,0:09:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草太
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.63,0:09:39.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些腌罗卜很有口感
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.29,0:09:41.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,味道很不错喔  吃吃看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.63,0:09:43.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.97,0:09:46.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  碗不用洗没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.97,0:09:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待会我会一起洗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.47,0:09:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.81,0:10:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.25,0:10:00.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈…\N姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.68,0:10:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.42,0:10:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要做什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.26,0:10:09.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.76,0:10:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道妈妈都不担心姐姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.33,0:10:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个腌罗卜真的很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.02,0:10:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.72,0:10:39.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出院了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.52,0:10:43.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次是身体\N出现了不明的斑点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.79,0:10:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装病的理由跟点子用光了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.79,0:10:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂且不管这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.53,0:10:50.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之后如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.33,0:10:51.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再装傻啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.03,0:10:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是和先前明明脚踏两条船
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.67,0:10:57.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又爱吃醋的\N粗暴任性男人的关系呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.11,0:10:58.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实的分手了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.74,0:11:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.24,0:11:04.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们好像说了什么不该说的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.39,0:11:14.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎狠狠的被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.36,0:11:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是戈薇甩掉他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.89,0:11:20.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说来…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.06,0:11:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还喜欢着那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.00,0:11:27.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过呢  已经完全没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:29.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经不在意了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.57,0:11:33.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  所以就什么都别再问了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.57,0:11:34.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.08,0:11:37.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是再碰触伤口的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:38.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.71,0:11:40.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种假笑好恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.52,0:11:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.92,0:11:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇跟钢牙要好一点就发脾气
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.43,0:11:56.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己却一心一意的跟桔梗跑掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:11:58.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就为了这么轻率的理由吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.10,0:12:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  去见戈薇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.94,0:12:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗唆耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.44,0:12:06.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经决定再也不去见她了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:10.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有搞错啊  你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.38,0:12:14.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是要你取回被戈薇姑娘\N带回去的四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:16.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你能通过那口井吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只为了四魂碎片?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意思是戈薇怎么样无所谓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.62,0:12:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也没有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.46,0:12:27.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉已经选择了桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.76,0:12:31.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要戈薇姑娘回来才是残酷的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.47,0:12:38.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉啊  这样真的妥当吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.41,0:12:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啦  枫姥姥连你也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.64,0:12:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的桔梗姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.48,0:12:46.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是由骨灰与土所创造的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.85,0:12:49.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就是不属于\N这个世界的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.28,0:12:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这样  魂魄还是桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:56.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不明白吗  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:12:59.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追根究底\N你们在这世上是无法结合的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.66,0:13:03.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗姐姐想要的\N只是和你共赴黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.00,0:13:07.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无所谓  就如桔梗所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:09.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和她一同下地狱去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.67,0:13:14.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那是我与桔梗的命运…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:30.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉碎片得拿去还他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:33.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要…我好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.47,0:13:39.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果归还这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.47,0:13:40.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就再也见不到犬夜叉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:44.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.21,0:13:46.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要跟随桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想听那些话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.85,0:13:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.42,0:13:57.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有桔梗的话就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…是这么坏的女人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.57,0:14:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在的表情一定很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.74,0:14:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的表情不能和犬夜叉相见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.38,0:14:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碎片…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.83,0:14:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神木
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.83,0:14:48.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了…这棵树
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.27,0:14:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是  将犬夜叉封印的树吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.28,0:14:55.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五百年前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:15:00.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这里  第一次遇见犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.78,0:15:03.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那什么呆滞的表情啊  桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.55,0:15:06.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经老的痴呆了吗  桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:09.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就一箭解决它啊  桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.29,0:15:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像上次解决我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.43,0:15:13.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.00,0:15:16.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗桔梗的  到底在叫谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.30,0:15:18.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听好了\N我的名字叫做…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.57,0:15:24.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.44,0:15:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:30.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.82,0:15:35.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.83,0:15:46.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我要和他相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:50.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早知道这么痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:53.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如当初不要相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.34,0:15:56.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我想见他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:16:01.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想再一次见到犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:10.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我竟然喜欢上犬夜叉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:17.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知何时  变得这么喜欢他了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:28.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.01,0:16:34.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.65,0:16:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.89,0:16:54.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.46,0:16:58.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当你待在神木的旁边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.73,0:17:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有感受到什么\N不可思议的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.54,0:17:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仿佛自己变的更诚实
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:08.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不觉得自己的心思\N也愈来愈清晰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.54,0:17:12.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当年接受你爸爸求婚的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.61,0:17:14.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.25,0:17:17.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈当然很喜欢你爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.92,0:17:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是求婚前几天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.42,0:17:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却为了一点琐事吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.42,0:17:24.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于能不能顺利的往下发展
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.43,0:17:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.43,0:17:28.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是一走到这棵树下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.70,0:17:30.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己也变的更加诚实
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.07,0:17:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是就OK了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.43,0:17:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏如此  得到了戈薇与草太
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.77,0:17:38.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈很感谢这棵树
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.78,0:17:43.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈不会过问戈薇在烦恼什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是妈妈相信戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.71,0:17:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为戈薇是会朝自己\N深信的道路勇往直前的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.05,0:17:54.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.66,0:18:01.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.66,0:18:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了  我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.43,0:18:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都还没说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.07,0:18:09.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我去见戈薇对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.30,0:18:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然知道为什么不去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是那就等于向戈薇道别了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.31,0:18:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候没能说出口的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.38,0:18:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须要传达给她才行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.22,0:18:25.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在最痛苦的人不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.22,0:18:27.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是戈薇姑娘才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.72,0:18:29.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.16,0:18:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉是已经下定决心了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.73,0:18:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我想戈薇现在一定非常苦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.96,0:18:37.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是男人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.93,0:18:40.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就去找戈薇把话说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.43,0:18:41.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漂亮的做个了结
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.00,0:18:45.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的  什么事都拖拖拉拉的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.47,0:18:49.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们…巴不得我和戈薇分开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:52.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不想分开吗\N你不想分开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.01,0:18:56.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨…谁会在意这种小事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.18,0:18:59.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经决定要保护桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.02,0:19:01.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的我怎能再说出
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.26,0:19:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到戈薇身边这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.19,0:19:05.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.46,0:19:09.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不到黄河心不死的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.76,0:19:12.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后就叫他劈腿男吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.70,0:19:14.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还比他振作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.20,0:19:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.24,0:19:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.51,0:19:25.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能说“回来吧”这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.98,0:19:28.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇应该很清楚才对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:30.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.82,0:19:32.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有好好的见个面道别的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.46,0:19:35.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我心里也放不下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.27,0:19:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.78,0:20:01.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在对面的这期间  我一直在想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.58,0:20:05.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  桔梗还有我的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.15,0:20:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  其实我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.82,0:20:09.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我了解的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.26,0:20:12.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为了解犬夜叉的心情  所以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.66,0:20:15.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我已经不能再待在这了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.56,0:20:17.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.27,0:20:20.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在遇到你之前  谁都不信任我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.07,0:20:25.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  你会为了我而掉泪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.34,0:20:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是待在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.04,0:20:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和戈薇在一起我很快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.58,0:20:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也很安心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.28,0:20:35.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我无法时而高兴时而欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.85,0:20:37.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗她…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.85,0:20:40.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗追随着我而死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.82,0:20:45.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此我必须舍命报答桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.06,0:20:49.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我比不上桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.36,0:20:52.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…我还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.30,0:20:58.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也考虑了许多桔梗的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.31,0:21:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗与我是完全不一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.31,0:21:05.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使说我是桔梗的转世
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.88,0:21:08.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我毕竟不是桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.38,0:21:12.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心是我自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.82,0:21:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过\N我只能理解一种桔梗的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.62,0:21:19.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.59,0:21:23.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望能再见犬夜叉一面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.10,0:21:26.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.83,0:21:30.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一想到桔梗\N也和我有相同的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.90,0:21:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就觉得轻松点了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.37,0:21:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然想要相见的心情是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.41,0:21:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才鼓起勇气来见犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.62,0:21:42.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.95,0:21:46.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我也很想见你一面  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.92,0:21:49.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和犬夜叉在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.16,0:21:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我无法忘记你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.64,0:22:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇…我该怎么回答才好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.44,0:22:11.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.21,0:22:14.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问你一件事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.66,0:22:25.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能和你在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.39,0:22:31.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要…和我在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.97,0:22:36.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉与桔梗的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.17,0:22:38.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不可能斩断的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.17,0:22:40.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点我清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.94,0:22:45.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是犬夜叉  我是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.15,0:22:49.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你相遇绝对不是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.65,0:22:54.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望犬夜叉能继续活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.99,0:22:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.33,0:23:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.50,0:23:06.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你开心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.17,0:23:09.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你充满欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.25,0:23:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道能为你做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.72,0:23:26.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我想一直待在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.89,0:23:49.70,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,除了真正珍贵的东西{\fad(500,0)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.04,0:24:01.18,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,若能全都舍弃 那该多好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.28,0:24:08.62,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,只是现实 往往是如此残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.59,0:24:12.36,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,但每当 遇到这种时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.36,0:24:17.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要紧闭双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.10,0:24:24.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,便能看见 你的笑容{\fad(0,900)}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.67,0:24:31.31,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,Ah- 但愿从此以往
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.15,0:24:38.89,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,直到进入 沉眠的那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.62,0:24:46.36,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,你的 那抹笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.03,0:24:54.60,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,都绝没有 消逝的瞬间{\fad(0,900)}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.79,0:25:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,投靠亲切的老爷爷\N与老婆婆的琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.76,0:25:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪竟然追来了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.99,0:25:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标是夺取背上的四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.80,0:25:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶然遇上的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.33,0:25:18.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将琥珀藏了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.03,0:25:21.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是琥珀完全想不起来
